    "gp_section_539438827849122720": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "c2e8772395e08c676a6310ab1560281d9b38288c2ccd3ba9db9622e5bad1622d_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-73gZF5zW_text": "<p>Emily Harper, a busy mom-to-be, calls it her 'lifesaver pillow' that lets her finally sleep pain-free despite the aches and discomfort of pregnancy. And with an <strong>average review rating of 4.8/5</strong>, you can join thousands of relieved moms-to-be and experience the comfort for yourself.</p>",
        "gg2LaW1VJvl_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-41f8427a-bb01-4737-82f7-132f7617055e.jpg",
        "gg2qZPIuUUs_text": "<p>Don't just take our word for it—listen to the stories of those who have found relief with the SmoothSpine Pillow.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggAhv73T2Jf_text": "3. Save Your Hips, Lower Back, and Your Wallet",
        "ggB86BrHfQK_text": "<p><strong>The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow is proven to alleviate back pain, hip pain, and Sciatica from night one,</strong> allowing you to sleep pain-free through the night.</p>",
        "ggCNBrRdBpV_text": "7. Over 26,619 Happy Side-Sleeping Mothers and Counting!",
        "ggDZAiqcrRI_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine pillow is specifically designed to address various conditions such as Sciatica, Bursitis, Piriformis, Stenosis, and Herniated Discs.</p>",
        "ggEM0g5yOx6_text": "1. Relieves Hips &amp; Back for Pain-Free Sleep During Pregnancy",
        "ggGX5lZ63k5_text": "8. It comes with a 90-Night 100% Money Back Guarantee",
        "ggGhYwfdjRu_text": "8. It comes with a 90-Night 100% Money Back Guarantee",
        "ggHNKMbxqgr_text": "2. More support &amp; comfort than a regular pillow",
        "ggHdYhfxOR2_text": "<p>Many solutions to hip and back pain can cost a fortune, but the SmoothSpine pillow offers a truly effective and affordable alternative.</p>",
        "ggHuA27YhjJ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-83057323-3900-4dd1-a2d4-474dd12e9a6f.jpg",
        "ggIeKd5gALX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-c8f9c6b3-59ee-483c-941e-8120e24e7bfa.jpg",
        "ggJTYNwrO5S_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-eec39d31-f2c0-48f5-add4-e1816fee1f5d.jpg",
        "ggK6av6M4lU_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/a6ec4f34946840609fcc0f61ebea0794.mp4",
        "ggK6av6M4lU_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggK6av6M4lU_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggKEzQg9ZNA_text": "4. Say Goodbye To Sciatica",
        "ggKufoAOt37_text": "<p>Many women have tried to sleep with old and bulky pillows between their legs, often without much success. You either lose it at night, don’t support your body properly, or simply get annoyed by how big and awkward it is.</p>",
        "ggNwVMknzGA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-2de29042-342f-42ef-87ad-3df621be0e03.jpg",
        "ggO1j_QJqoF_text": "<p>We're so confident you'll love the SmoothSpine pillow, <strong>you can try it risk-free for 90 days. </strong>If you're not satisfied in any way, simply reach out to our helpful support team, and we’ll refund you every penny you paid. And with our extremely low return rate of 1.2%, we think it’s highly unlikely you will…</p>",
        "ggO4voaWbF2_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine pillow is<strong> designed to be used in between your legs, stays with you all night, and doesn’t take up any additional space in bed.&nbsp;</strong></p>",
        "ggPdWmTTiK7_text": "<p>By keeping your spine and hips naturally aligned and relieving pressure on joints and nerves, the SmoothSpine pillow helps your body activate its self-healing process — giving you natural relief without any side effects.</p>",
        "ggQSCroEjl0_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8133079b-601b-4441-ae34-aeb325db676c.png",
        "ggT4fqEiOgj_text": "2. Better support &amp; More comfort than regular pillows",
        "ggVhXJ6AU6h_text": "<p>SmoothSpine provides a remarkable solution that doesn’t just ease your nighttime discomfort — it restores your energy and freedom to enjoy the activities you love every day.</p>",
        "ggWL7SdHihi_text": "4. Say Goodbye To Sciatica",
        "ggZnWy8qjRx_text": "<p>Olivia Bennett, an expecting mom, said this during her third trimester: 'Before this pillow, I couldn’t get comfortable—every time I shifted, my regular pillow would move, waking me up all night. Now, I sleep through the night and wake up feeling like myself again.</p>",
        "ggaHhxGHW5W_text": "7. Over 57,619 Happy Side-Sleepers and Counting!",
        "ggdqzzO03ju_text": "6. Get Back To The Life You Deserve",
        "ggfgFiPQYwE_text": "5. Natural Pain Relief",
        "ggi4CgFqPHM_text": "<p>This results in longer lasting relief, uninterrupted sleep, and more comfort.</p>",
        "ggjskyumgvh_text": "<p>While popular treatments may set you back $100s each month, the SmoothSpine pillow provides a similar effectiveness at a fraction of the cost—making it accessible to everyone. Depending on your usage, this pillow lasts for years. Making it the perfect long-term solution!</p>",
        "ggm8Gr97rT9_text": "3. Save Your Hips, Lower Back, and Your Wallet",
        "ggoJPVYUOGg_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine pillow is designed to give you back your pain-free, restful sleep — so you can focus on enjoying every moment of this special time in your life.</p>",
        "ggq2utr2w82_text": "1. Relieves Hips &amp; Back for Pain-Free Sleep",
        "ggqgRlWjSXo_text": "<p>By providing comfortable all night support and proper spinal alignment, the SmoothSpine pillow helps to actively alleviate pinched nerves, stiff joints, and tense muscles, leading to better hip, lower back, and even knee health.</p>",
        "ggrNoWvp0nI_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-d303fac0-837e-48fe-b716-f385d7da44d9.png",
        "gguIBMActN6_text": "6. Get Back To Enjoying Your Pregnancy Journey",
        "ggwe38B6rwl_text": "<p>Pregnancy is a beautiful journey, and the same time it can come with its own share of aches and pains—especially in the hips, lower back, and legs.</p>",
        "ggyDW284IuO_text": "<p>Side sleeping is considered the safest for you and your baby. And with the SmoothSpine Pillow, getting relief is as easy as placing it between your legs and laying on your side! No complicated stretches, no extra doctor visits, and no medication required!</p>",
        "ggyGNjGvxz__text": "<p>Unlike risky medications, the SmoothSpine pillow offers a natural and effortless way to relieve pain. With its soft elastic strap, perfect balance of firmness and comfort, cooling fabric, and ergonomic contoured design, many moms-to-be report waking up feeling relief from the very first night.</p>",
        "ggzNRYWR_oA_text": "5. Natural Pain Relief"
      },
